WEBVTT

00:02:26.778 --> 00:02:30.804
DK: Yes, under Nazi occupation
in [unclear] Southern France,

00:02:30.828 --> 00:02:32.300
running away from them,

00:02:32.324 --> 00:02:34.039
and I had a lot of time to myself

00:02:34.063 --> 00:02:37.345
because I didn't go
to school all the time.

00:02:37.369 --> 00:02:40.894
There were periods where it was
too dangerous to go to school,

00:02:40.918 --> 00:02:43.346
so I was quite
an introspective little boy.

00:02:43.370 --> 00:02:47.488
But I was thinking
about psychology, really.

00:02:47.512 --> 00:02:49.841
CA: Well, and something
amazing happened in Paris

00:02:49.865 --> 00:02:51.754
that you've spoken about before.

00:02:52.163 --> 00:02:55.568
DK: So I was seven years old,

00:02:55.592 --> 00:03:00.898
it was 1941, there was a curfew for Jews,